{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/blog/amadas","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"amadas"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Branding for Smart Doorlock Company, Amadas","author":"Minkyoung Lee, Hanjin Cho","date":"March 18th, 2017","hero_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.4150943396226414,"src":"/static/1d65d2efb2d4062b2c3426d1f2d4934e/398d8/amadas-1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/1d65d2efb2d4062b2c3426d1f2d4934e/8def4/amadas-1.jpg 375w,\n/static/1d65d2efb2d4062b2c3426d1f2d4934e/35c3d/amadas-1.jpg 750w,\n/static/1d65d2efb2d4062b2c3426d1f2d4934e/398d8/amadas-1.jpg 1500w,\n/static/1d65d2efb2d4062b2c3426d1f2d4934e/0e37b/amadas-1.jpg 2250w,\n/static/1d65d2efb2d4062b2c3426d1f2d4934e/0aeb3/amadas-1.jpg 2835w","sizes":"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px"}}}},"html":"<p>We made logo, design guideline and promotion 3D animation for a smart doorlock company, Amadas. I was a project manager of this project. An exclusive font is made for Amadas's identity design. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Client | AMADAS</li>\n<li>Cowork | Minkyoung Lee (designer), Hanjin Cho (3D animator)</li>\n<li>Duration | 1 month</li>\n<li>Responsibility | project management, brand design, font development, identity guideline production, directing video production</li>\n<li>Tools | Sketch, Illustrator, Photoshop, Premiere Pro</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Their previous logo was too rigid and masculine. It did not go well with the company's delicate form. I manufactured a font based on 'Optima' to express Amadas's sophisticated high tech and the integrative nature of art and technology. It was developed by adding a curved surface following the motif from the shape of the handle to the font Optima's basic solidity and structure.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-b